SpaceShooter is an old-school space shooter game in 2D.
Copyright (C) 2010 Alessandro Ghedini <al3xbio@gmail.com>

Version 2.0

This software is released under GNU GPL licence v.3
This program comes with ABSOLUTELY NO WARRANTY. This is free software, 
and you are welcome to redistribute it under certain conditions.

To be compiled it needs Allegro shared library (liballegro4.2) 
and its development files (liballegro4.2-dev).

=== Compile & Install ===
$ make
# make install

=== Run ===
$ SpaceShooter
